                            <comment id="13462015" author="henrique" created="Mon, 24 Sep 2012 19:07:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think you have a good point and I&apos;m committing it but it unfortunately doesn&apos;t fix the TBufferedTransport.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;e.g.&lt;br/&gt;
thrift/test/nodejs$ timeout 2 make server &amp;amp; sleep 1; make client &lt;br/&gt;
only runs one or two tests before stopping/crashing when using TBufferedTransport.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
